#: .\units\archaic_units\menagerie\Little_Green_Man.cfg:19
#: .\units\archaic_units\menagerie\Little_Green_Soldier.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The Magnellian civilization reached many worlds before encountering the one "
"that would be its undoing. Roswellians are short, stocky, apparently "
"genderless humanoids with big black eyes set in a big bald head. Despite an "
"almost child-like appearance, these odd beings are not vulnerable, for they "
"can lash out with some sort of supernatural ability."
msgstr ""

